1. Install CLI
a. If Windows 64 bit : https://sfdc.co/sfdx_cli_win64
b. If Windows 32 bit : https://sfdc.co/sfdx_cli_win
c. If Mac : https://sfdc.co/sfdx_cli_osx
d. Once installation is completed, to check type "sfdx" in command prompt.

2. Install JDK8 or JdK11 and set the path. 
To set path: Goto Environment variables=> System variables=> Copy BIN path of JDK and paste into path.

3. In VS code, To write SFDX commands you have 2 options:
Option 1: Write your complete command on Terminal.
Option 2: To auto create command, Ctrl+Shift+P
